51
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:26,480
Fine.

52
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,200
Stop talking nonsense.

53
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,320
I know him better than you.

54
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:33,280
If you were to...

55
