56
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,680
we wouldn’t be able...

57
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,800
to buy food anymore.

58
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:38,440
Would you buy us food?

59
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,880
What?

60
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:41,880
